genresAdvancedInfo.name: reading
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Reading is a genre of music that is characterized by its calming and relaxing qualities. It is often used for meditation, yoga, or as background music for reading or studying. Reading music is typically instrumental and features gentle melodies, soothing sounds, and minimal percussion.
